		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Lift Arm:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick Up</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Retract Arm:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick Down</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Turn left or right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick Left or Right</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Lower Boom:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button or Right Analog Stick Up</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Lift Boom:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button or Right Analog Stick Down</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Scoop Bucket:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button or Right Analog Stick Left</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Lift Bucket:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button or Right Analog Stick Right</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
