          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES (Go to 'Get it with the Power Shovel' in the main menu and purchase the following items for the desired effects):</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Unlock a hidden minigame -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "New Part Timer 3" for $500,000</font>&nbsp;
