			<br>&nbsp; Unlock a hidden minigame -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "New Part Timer 1" for $600,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock more credits -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Continue Credit 2 Credits" for 2 additional credits. The price doubles each time and starts at $200,00</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock hidden movie -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Movie Vol. 1" for $5,000,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the fifth part of the Photo Gallery -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Photo Vol. 5" for $200,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the first part of the BGM section of the Sound Test -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Vol. 1 BGM" for $300,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the first part of the Photo Gallery -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Photo Vol. 1" for $100,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the first part of the Spoken section of the Sound Test -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Voice 1" for $300,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the forth part of the Photo Gallery -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Photo Vol. 4" for $200,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the game mode "Technician Mode - Time Trial" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Techinician Mode" for $10,000,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the second part of the BGM section of the Sound Test -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Vol. 2 BGM" for $300,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the second part of the Photo Gallery -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Purchase "Photo Vol. 2" for $100,000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the second part of the Spoken section of the Sound Test -
